description.from:
Serializer to be used in API docs for update operations where los_loan_id is provided in the url, not as parameter.
Go for details to the ticket: https://pollyex.atlassian.net/browse/APP-19099

Enumerated list of Investor Experience types. ENUM: ['NotApplicable', 'ExperiencedInvestor', 'FirstTimeInvestor']. Indicates the experience level of the real estate investor as it applies to DSCR.

* `ExperiencedInvestor` - ExperiencedInvestor
* `FirstTimeInvestor` - FirstTimeInvestor
